snippet: Vasily G. Aleksanyan, a Yukos executive and lawyer who was swept up in the politically tinged prosecution of the Yukos oil empire, died at his home in Moscow on Monday, news outlets reported.
lead_paragraph: Vasily G. Aleksanyan, a Yukos executive and lawyer who was swept up in the politically tinged prosecution of the Yukos oil empire, died at his home in Moscow on Monday, news outlets reported.

headline.seo: Former Yukos Lawyer Vasily Aleksanyan Dies
